	<page pageno="0">
		<para>Where is the cake?</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="1">
		<para>A cake is hid/ing. Where?</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="2">
		<para>Mi/na and Peng look at the map, for clues.</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="3">
		<para>Then Peng looks un/der the ta/ble.</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="4">
		<para>No cake there!</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="5">
		<para>Mi/na looks up the tree.</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="6">
		<para>No cake there!</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="7">
		<para>Mi/na and Peng look at the map a/gain.</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="8">
		<para>They look be/hind the bush.</para>
	</page>
	<page pageno="9">
		<para>There is the cake!</para>
	</page>
</book>
